From 0580f284b7bb2a0be88ff7b3760a7c9dc91355dc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Balamurugan Ramar <quic_bramar@quicinc.com>
Date: Thu, 10 Apr 2025 23:26:19 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] mac80211: wifi athk Enable lock less tx netdevice flag

dev_fast_xmit spends more CPU cylces on spinlock before calling
ieee80211_subif_start_xmit_8023. Avoid the lock by enabling
NETIF_F_LLTX flag in netdev feature flag.

This lock less netdev tx provides 1GB throughput improvement
incase of 2link MLO.

Signed-off-by: P Praneesh <quic_ppranees@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Balamurugan Ramar <quic_bramar@quicinc.com>
---
 net/mac80211/ieee80211_i.h | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/net/mac80211/ieee80211_i.h b/net/mac80211/ieee80211_i.h
index 29240f0..d57371c 100644
--- a/net/mac80211/ieee80211_i.h
+++ b/net/mac80211/ieee80211_i.h
@@ -2068,7 +2068,7 @@ void ieee80211_color_collision_detection_work(struct wiphy *wiphy,
 #define MAC80211_SUPPORTED_FEATURES_TX	(NETIF_F_IP_CSUM | NETIF_F_IPV6_CSUM | \
 					 NETIF_F_HW_CSUM | NETIF_F_SG | \
 					 NETIF_F_HIGHDMA | NETIF_F_GSO_SOFTWARE | \
-					 NETIF_F_HW_TC)
+					 NETIF_F_LLTX)
 #define MAC80211_SUPPORTED_FEATURES_RX	(NETIF_F_RXCSUM)
 #define MAC80211_SUPPORTED_FEATURES	(MAC80211_SUPPORTED_FEATURES_TX | \
 					 MAC80211_SUPPORTED_FEATURES_RX)
-- 
